<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Platform fighting game <em><a title="Games > Rivals of Aether II [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/rivals-of-aether-ii">Rivals of Aether II</a></em> will add Gouie, “The Lost Mireling” as its next free additional character update on August 4, developer <a title="Companies > Aether Studios [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/aether-studios">Aether Studios</a> announced. The titular protagonist from <a title="Companies > Yacht Club Games [50 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/yacht-club-games">Yacht Club Games</a>‘ <em><a title="Games > Mina the Hollower [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mina-the-hollower">Mina the Hollower</a></em> will follow as a guest character in 2027. <span id="more-1061630"></span></p><p><em>Rivals of Aether II</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2217000/Rivals_of_Aether_II/" target="_blank">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch a new set of trailers below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Gouie, The Lost Mireling</span></h2><p><iframe title="Gouie: The Lost Mireling | Official Character Trailer - Rivals of Aether II" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gVCjCZe_HHA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><h2><span>Character Teaser: Mina the Hollower</span></h2><!-- AD: content -->
